      - Conversion Likelihood
  → Standard users: score hidden, content silently improved
  → Pro users: full Pre-cog dashboard visible
      "Predicted top 5 ranking within 60 days"
      "Low GEO citation probability — restructure H2s"
```

*Free users feel the platform is better. They just don't know why. That's the upgrade hook.*

